line_2: In the caverns of the west,
In the caverns of the west,

line_1: Again the Parent's pointed Jaws comprest
line_2: By Force expell them from their pleasing Rest.

line_1: By cruel Gripe the passive Wretch comprest
line_2: Twines up her Tail, and rears her shining Breast.

line_1: A frozen clod, by death's cold hand comprest,
line_2: Each quiv'ring nerve and throbbing pulse at rest;

line_1: The young Narcissus, in it's bulb compress'd,
line_2: Cradles a second nestling on its breast;

line_1: The man of bus'ness and his friends compress'd,
line_2: Forget their labours, and yet find no rest;
